<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" dir="ltr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>400 - Bad Request | IslamWiki</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Amiri:wght@400;700&family=Noto+Sans:wght@400;500;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f8fafc 0%, #e2e8f0 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .error-container {
            background: white;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 20px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            padding: 60px;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 700px;
            width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .error-container::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            height: 6px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #dc2626, #ef4444, #f87171);
        }

        .error-icon {
            font-size: 4rem;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            animation: pulse 2s infinite;
        }

        @keyframes pulse {
            0%, 100% { transform: scale(1); }
            50% { transform: scale(1.1); }
        }

        .error-code {
            font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
            font-size: 6rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #dc2626;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.2);
        }

        .error-title {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #1f2937;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .error-message {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            line-height: 1.6;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
        }

        .error-details {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
            text-align: left;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .error-details h3 {
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .error-details ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .error-details li {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 12px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .error-details li:last-child {
            border-bottom: none;
        }

        .error-details .label {
            font-weight: 500;
            color: #374151;
            min-width: 120px;
        }

        .error-details .value {
            color: #6b7280;
            font-family: 'Courier New', monospace;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            word-break: break-all;
            text-align: right;
            flex: 1;
            margin-left: 20px;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 15px;
            justify-content: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            margin-bottom: 40px;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 14px 28px;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 500;
            text-decoration: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
            min-width: 140px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .btn-primary {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1e40af, #3b82f6);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-primary:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(30, 64, 175, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-secondary {
            background: #f3f4f6;
            color: #374151;
            border: 2px solid #d1d5db;
        }

        .btn-secondary:hover {
            background: #e5e7eb;
            border-color: #9ca3af;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
        }

        .btn-danger {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #dc2626, #ef4444);
            color: white;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.3);
        }

        .btn-danger:hover {
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(220, 38, 38, 0.4);
        }

        .btn .button-text {
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn .loading {
            position: absolute;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s ease;
        }

        .btn.loading .button-text {
            opacity: 0;
        }

        .btn.loading .loading {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        .islamic-quote {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fef3c7, #fde68a);
            border-radius: 15px;
            padding: 30px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 6px solid #f59e0b;
        }

        .quote-text {
            font-family: 'Amiri', serif;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #92400e;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            font-style: italic;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .quote-source {
            color: #a16207;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .technical-info {
            background: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 12px;
            padding: 25px;
            border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        }

        .technical-info h4 {
            color: #374151;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .technical-info p {
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .technical-info ul {
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-left: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .technical-info li {
            margin-bottom: 8px;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            .error-container {
                padding: 40px 30px;
                margin: 20px;
            }

            .error-code {
                font-size: 4rem;
            }

            .error-title {
                font-size: 1.5rem;
            }

            .action-buttons {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: center;
            }

            .btn {
                width: 100%;
                max-width: 300px;
            }

            .error-details li {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
                gap: 5px;
            }

            .error-details .value {
                text-align: left;
                margin-left: 0;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="error-container">
        <!-- Error Icon -->
        <div class="error-icon">⚠️</div>
        
        <!-- Error Code -->
        <div class="error-code">400</div>
        
        <!-- Error Title -->
        <h1 class="error-title">Bad Request</h1>
        
        <!-- Error Message -->
        <p class="error-message">
            The request could not be understood by the server due to malformed syntax. Please check your request and try again.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Error Details -->
        <div class="error-details">
            <h3>Request Information</h3>
            <ul>
                <li>
                    <span class="label">Time:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ timestamp|default('now'|date('Y-m-d H:i:s T')) }}</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="label">URL:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ request_url|default(app.request.uri|default('Unknown')) }}</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="label">Method:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ request_method|default(app.request.method|default('Unknown')) }}</span>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <span class="label">IP Address:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ client_ip|default(app.request.clientIp|default('Unknown')) }}</span>
                </li>
                {% if app.debug %}
                <li>
                    <span class="label">Error:</span>
                    <span class="value">{{ error_message|default('Bad request syntax') }}</span>
                </li>
                {% endif %}
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Action Buttons -->
        <div class="action-buttons">
            <a href="{{ path('home') }}" class="btn btn-primary">
                <span class="button-text">Go to Homepage</span>
                <span class="loading">↻</span>
            </a>
            <button onclick="window.history.back()" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <span class="button-text">Go Back</span>
                <span class="loading">↻</span>
            </button>
            <button onclick="location.reload()" class="btn btn-secondary">
                <span class="button-text">Try Again</span>
                <span class="loading">↻</span>
            </button>
            <a href="{{ path('contact')|default('#') }}" class="btn btn-danger">
                <span class="button-text">Report Issue</span>
                <span class="loading">↻</span>
            </a>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Islamic Quote -->
        <div class="islamic-quote">
            <div class="quote-text">
                "And when you speak, be just, even if it be against a near relative."
            </div>
            <div class="quote-source">
                — Quran 6:152
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Technical Information -->
        <div class="technical-info">
            <h4>What happened?</h4>
            <p>The server could not understand your request due to:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Malformed URL or parameters</li>
                <li>Invalid request format</li>
                <li>Missing required fields</li>
                <li>Syntax errors in the request</li>
            </ul>
            
            <h4 style="margin-top: 1rem;">What you can do:</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Check the URL for typos or errors</li>
                <li>Verify all required form fields are filled</li>
                <li>Try refreshing the page</li>
                <li>Contact support if the problem persists</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <script>
        // Button loading states
        document.querySelectorAll('.btn').forEach(btn => {
            btn.addEventListener('click', function() {
                if (this.tagName === 'A') {
                    this.classList.add('loading');
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        this.classList.remove('loading');
                    }, 2000);
                }
            });
        });

        // Console logging for debugging
        console.log('400 Bad Request Error Page Loaded');
        console.log('Error Details:', {
            timestamp: '{{ timestamp|default("now"|date("Y-m-d H:i:s T")) }}',
            url: '{{ request_url|default(app.request.uri|default("Unknown")) }}',
            method: '{{ request_method|default(app.request.method|default("Unknown")) }}',
            client_ip: '{{ client_ip|default(app.request.clientIp|default("Unknown")) }}'
        });

        // Analytics tracking (if available)
        if (typeof gtag !== 'undefined') {
            gtag('event', 'error_page_view', {
                'error_code': '400',
                'error_type': 'bad_request',
                'page_title': '400 Bad Request'
            });
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html> 